            "id": 6422122,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 南電(8046)大漲7.16%，報703元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>南電(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8046:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8046\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8046-TW</a>)16日11:00股價上漲47元，報703.0元，漲幅7.16%，成交16,423張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>南電(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8046:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8046\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8046-TW</a>)所屬產業為電子零組件業，主要業務為CC01080電子零組件製造業。CC01090電池製造業。ZZ99999除許可業務外,得經營法令非禁止或限制之業務。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲2.98%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲5.64%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+2,147 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+511 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+2,217 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-581 張</li> <li>融資增減：-492 張</li> <li>融券增減：-33 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6422122",
